                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As a Bard player (level 60), please dont take this the wrong way, but you are a little off with the facts.
<br />
1. I cant think of a bard DS that stacks with a Bard DS. Then again, if you go to eqdiva and make a search, someone already made a table of all the DS stacks and the max you can get from it.
<br />
2. We are jack of all trades and amster of none. True, the instruments make our songs very good, but without a group, those songs are not that great. We add to the groups DPS, but on our own we suck at it, heck we make casters look good.
<br />
3. Can we take the place of an enchanter? Yes, can we do as a good a job as an enchanter? (some bards are going to hate for this), no. We have very good group haste, but I much prefer the enchanters haste, I rather play an over haste. Why?, There are so many other songs I'de rather sing. Can we CC? Yes, but the max is 4 and then we cant play anything else. 
<br />
4. Please realize that their so much info on a bard that it is hard to know everything. That is why that when someone asked me and Im not sure, I refer them to other web sites. 
<br />
5. I palyed an enchanter before and I have nothing but admiration for the class. The fact that you CC wearing silk is just amazing. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />
6. Anybody that compares a bard with anybody else is plum locko. We dont take place of a class, we just make every other class better.
